Preconditions: During the test, we check the user with an email that appears in the database

Title: Login as an existing user, but modify the UserID
Preconditions:
During the test, we check the ability to log in to an existing user with a changed login name
Change in User ID : mngr484054 the letter ""g"" to ""G"" => login for login : mnGr484054

Preconditions:
During the test, we check the ability to log in to an existing user with a modified password
in Password we change the sixth letter from uppercase ""A"" to lowercase ""a""
